text: puokke ban tb vinh tha ao sahou eb. puok yeung minsauv yl chraen te nouv avei del anak niyeay haey pitabrakd nasa yeung meul kheunh anakchea anak tnkhsaaoy nowknongchamnaom puok yeung . haey brasenbae kmean kruosaear anak te noh puok yeung nung kb anak nung dom thm tow haey . haey anak minmen chea anak khlang samreab puok yeung laey
